==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
From Low German ''[[Kraanbere]]'', from ''[[Kraan#Low_German|Kraan]]'' "crane" + ''[[Bere#Low_German|Bere]]'' "berry".
===Noun===
{{en-noun|cranberr|ies}}

#A red [[cowberry]], used to make cranberry sauce.

